OL,5, The buy now, pay later firm Klarna is  
OL,6, extending its services, including      
OL,7, offering the choice of paying for items
OL,8, in full, immediately.                  
OL,10,FIt said the "pay now" option and other 
OL,11,Fchanges it was making would give       
OL,12,Fcustomers more clarity and control.    
OL,14,F"Most of the time people should pay    
OL,15,Fwith the money they have," said        
OL,16,FKlarna's chief executive.              
OL,18,FBuy now, pay later firms like Klarna   
OL,19,Fhave seen business boom over the last  
OL,20,Ffew years.                             
